---
import BaseCN from "../../layouts/BaseCN.astro";
import ShapeFooter from "../../components/ShapeFooter.astro";
---

<BaseCN
  title="寻找 NocoBase 合作伙伴 - 全球服务网络为你的项目保驾护航"
  description="NocoBase 拥有遍布全球的合作伙伴网络，提供专业的系统开发、系统集成与技术运维支持服务。提交你的需求，我们为你匹配最合适的服务伙伴。"
  keywords="NocoBase 合作伙伴, 寻找伙伴, 系统开发, 系统集成, 技术运维, 服务实施"
>
  <!-- Hero/Banner Start -->
  <section class="bg-half-170 bg-light d-table w-100">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 text-center">
          <div class="title-heading">
            <span class="badge bg-soft-primary mb-3">寻找合作伙伴</span>
            <h1 class="fw-bold mt-2 mb-3">找到合适的 NocoBase 伙伴，助你成功</h1>
            <p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted">NocoBase 拥有遍布全球的合作伙伴网络，提供基于 NocoBase 的系统开发、系统集成、部署运维等服务，为你的项目保驾护航。</p>
            <div class="mt-4 pt-2">
              <a href="#submit-requirements" class="btn btn-primary me-3">
                <i class="uil uil-file-edit-alt me-1"></i>提交需求
              </a>
              <a href="#partner-fit" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
                <i class="uil uil-arrow-down me-1"></i>了解详情
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- Hero/Banner End -->

  <!-- Partner Fit Start -->
  <section class="section" id="partner-fit">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2">
            <h4 class="title mb-3">哪些情况适合找合作伙伴</h4>
            <p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted mb-0">如果你正面临以下情况，NocoBase 合作伙伴可以帮助你更高效地推进项目落地。</p>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-users-alt rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4 d-flex flex-column">
              <h5 class="title text-dark mb-2">没有足够的内部开发团队</h5>
              <p class="text-muted">缺少熟悉企业应用搭建、交付与维护的团队时，可以借助伙伴快速补齐实施能力。</p>
              <i class="uil uil-users-alt full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-rocket rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4 d-flex flex-column">
              <h5 class="title text-dark mb-2">需要快速上线业务系统</h5>
              <p class="text-muted">当项目时间紧、需要尽快验证业务流程或交付系统时，伙伴服务能显著缩短建设周期。</p>
              <i class="uil uil-rocket full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-setting rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4 d-flex flex-column">
              <h5 class="title text-dark mb-2">需要定制开发、培训或运维服务</h5>
              <p class="text-muted">如果你不仅需要软件，还需要长期陪跑与支持，选择伙伴服务更加稳妥。</p>
              <i class="uil uil-setting full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- Partner Fit End -->

  <!-- Services Start -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2">
            <h4 class="title mb-4">NocoBase 伙伴能为你做什么</h4>
            <p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted mb-0">无论是全新开发还是现有系统升级，NocoBase 合作伙伴为你提供端到端的专业服务。</p>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-laptop-cloud rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4">
              <h5 class="title text-dark">系统开发</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">基于 NocoBase 平台进行定制化应用开发，满足你独特的业务需求。从需求分析、方案设计到开发交付，全流程专业服务。</p>
              <i class="uil uil-laptop-cloud full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-link-alt rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4">
              <h5 class="title text-dark">系统集成</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">将 NocoBase 与你现有的 ERP、CRM、OA 等系统无缝对接，打通数据孤岛，实现业务流程的自动化与统一管理。</p>
              <i class="uil uil-link-alt full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-setting rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4">
              <h5 class="title text-dark">技术运维支持</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">提供系统部署、升级维护、性能优化和故障排除等运维服务，确保你的 NocoBase 系统稳定高效运行。</p>
              <i class="uil uil-setting full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- Services End -->

  <!-- Submit Requirements Start -->
  <section class="section" id="submit-requirements">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
          <h4 class="title mb-4">提交你的需求</h4>
          <p class="text-muted para-desc mx-auto mb-4">
            告诉我们你的项目需求，我们将匹配最合适的 NocoBase 伙伴，助力项目成功落地。
          </p>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10">
          <div class="card border-0 shadow rounded overflow-hidden">
            <iframe
              src="https://service-cn.nocobase.com/public-forms/qgont25zd77"
              style="width: 100%; min-height: 700px; border: none;"
              loading="lazy"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- Submit Requirements End -->

  <ShapeFooter />
</BaseCN>
